title: Friday AM Arktoons

content_html:
HYPERGAMOUSE Episode 16: I Hate That Guy

You may note that the dev team has made a few changes to the Arktoons interface, including the useful ability to choose between ascending and descending episodes, although the default remains a descending order in which the most recent episode in a series is displayed on top.
